<citebib id="Gideons"/> `a Jesús como salvación.´</t></rf></rb>
 to Israel according to his promise, 
<t lang="es"> Israel de acuerdo a su promesa, </t>
<sv num="24" id="Hechos-13-24"/>
before his coming, when John had first preached the baptism of repentance 
