cada sábado, y las cuales cumplieron al condenarlo.  </t>
<sv num="28" id="Hechos-13-28"/>
Though they found no cause for death, they still asked Pilate to have
him killed. 
<t lang="es">Aunque no encontraron causa para matarlo, pidieron a 
Pilato que lo asesinara. </t>
<sv num="29" id="Hechos-13-29"/>
When they had fulfilled all things that were written about
him, they took him down from the tree, and laid him in a tomb. 
<t lang="es">Cuando habían cumplido todas las cosas escritas sobre Él,
lo bajaron del madero y lo pusieron en una tumba. </t>
<sv num="30" id="Hechos-13-30"/>
But God raised him from the dead, 
