«hermanos o hermanas.»</t></rf>
</rb>
, that through this man is proclaimed to you
remission of sins, 
<t lang="es">, que por medio de este Hombre se proclama para ustedes
el perdón de los pecados, </t>
<sv num="39" id="Hechos-13-39"/>
and by him everyone who believes is justified from
all things, from which you<wi type="T">P</wi> could not be 
